messages.messageBody:
We are
Donanne Dean(39) Steve Hinman(37) Avalon (4) Nature(19mo)
Homebirthing, attachement parenting, co-sleeping, baby wearing, still
tandem nursing, cloth diapering, unschooling, organic gardening, no
vax , biodiesel fuel making and leaning towards very green living
family.
We live in Cape Elizabeth, ME
ph 207 899 1089

I am having an unschool playgroup at my house on wed aug 15th 1-5pm.

Directions:
Cross Casco Bay bridge (rt77) go straight at the light staying on rt
77. At the next light go right. There is a pizza joint and a sign
pointing to the right towards Cape Elizabeth and rt 77. Go three
lights up. This is Spurwinnk ave. Go left.
We are the tenth house on the right.
White house with light grey garrage and a camper trailer and I have a
black jetta tdi plastered with bumper stickers.
If you get to a stop sign then you have gone to far. We are three
houses back from the stop sign.
My phone number is 207 899 1089
email
ibex@...

We have a big organic garden out back with a big back yard and a
cedar works play set and a big hot tub.

Please bring naturel whole food snacks to share if you like.
Donanne
